==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sunwise
<hw>Sun"wise`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In the direction
of the sun's apparent motion, or from the east southward and westward,
and so around the circle; also, in the same direction as the movement of
the hands of a watch lying face upward.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

